      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its high-pressure double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies functioning in perfect synchronization. This specimen boasts a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission with crisp, short-throw engagement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is superlative, with zero subframe fatigue and a suspension geometry that remains factory-tight. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep factory luster with no evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
